Little Big Adventure Data Library
Version 0.1

This is a collection of C routines for reading data files from Little Big Adventure (Copyright 1994 by Adeline Software International) and Little Big Adventure 2 (Copyright 1997 by Adeline Software International).

It is mainly based on the seminal work of Vincent Hamm, who created a complete reimplementation of the game engine of Little Big Adventure (http://sourceforge.net/projects/twin-e/)
